            <div type="transcript" id="P96-115">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They won't frown always,  some sweet day</l>
                    <l>When I forget to tease,</l>
                    <l>They'll recollect how cold I looked,</l>
                    <l>And how I just said 'please.'</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then they will hasten to the door</l>
                    <l>To call the little child,</l>
                    <l>Who cannot thank them, for the ice</l>
                    <l>That on her lisping piled.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
